name: AtlantaAirport
0:
”Alexa, open Atlanta Airport.”
”Get airport status.”
”Get parking lot status.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: atlanta airport
des:
Get general information about Hartsfield–Jackson Atlanta International Airport. Information includes airport status, weather conditions, parking lot availability and security checkpoint wait estimates. 

Parking lot status information includes; International Hourly, International Park-Ride, North Daily, North Economy, North Hourly, Park-Ride-A, Park-Ride-C, South Daily, South Economy, South Hourly and West Economy. 

Security checkpoint estimates include International Checkpoint, Domestic Main Checkpoint, Domestic North Checkpoint and Domestic South Checkpoint.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
